==Accolades== {| class="wikitable plainrowheaders sortable" |- !scope="col"| Year !scope="col"| Award !scope="col"| Category !scope="col"| Nominated work !scope="col"| Result ! scope="col" class="unsortable"| {{Abbr|Ref(s)|Reference(s)}} |- |rowspan="3"| 2016 ! scope="row" rowspan="3"| [[7th Gaumee Film Awards]] | [[Gaumee Film Award for Best Supporting Actress|Best Supporting Actress]] | ''Loodhifa'' | {{won}} |style="text-align:center;"| <ref name=GFA7won/> |- | rowspan="2"| [[Gaumee Film Award for Best Makeup|Best Makeup]] | ''Loodhifa'' | {{nom}} |style="text-align:center;"|<ref name=GFA7nom>{{cite news|url=https://mihaaru.com/entertainment/10378 |title=Nominations for 7th Gaumee Film Awards Announced |language=Dhivehi |work=Mihaaru |last=Adhushan |first=Ahmed |date=16 December 2016 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180330160950/https://mihaaru.com/entertainment/28015 |deadurl=no |archivedate=30 March 2018 |accessdate=30 March 2018}}</ref> |- | ''[[Sazaa (2011 film)|Sazaa]]'' <small>(Shared with [[Niuma Mohamed]])</small> | {{nom}} |style="text-align:center;"|<ref name=GFA7nom/> |- | 2017 ! scope="row" | [[8th Gaumee Film Awards]] | [[Gaumee Film Award for Best Supporting Actress|Best Supporting Actress]] | ''Aadheys'' | {{nom}} |style="text-align:center;"|<ref name=GFA8nom>{{cite news|url=https://mihaaru.com/entertainment/28015 |title=8th Gaumee Film Awards: Dark Rain leads nomination |language=Dhivehi |work=Mihaaru |last=Adhushan |first=Ahmed |date=12 December 2017 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180330160950/https://mihaaru.com/entertainment/28015 |deadurl=no |archivedate=30 March 2018 |accessdate=30 March 2018}}</ref> |- |}
